// postman testing file

1. run project: new terminal -> npm run dev
2. Connect to MongoDB Compass: new connection -> URI: mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/gymapp
                                              -> Name: GymApp
3. Open Postman: URI: http://localhost:3000

--------------------------------------------------- EVENTS ---------------------------------------------------------

--- CREATE EVENT ---

URI: http://localhost:5000/service-event/api/events/addEvent
Method: POST

raw json:
    {
        "title": "Boxing for Beginners",
        "description": "Gentle stretching session",
        "date": "2025-12-05T18:00:00.000Z",
        "capacity": 15,
        "location": "Room B"
    }


--- GET ALL EVENTS ---
http://localhost:5000/service-event/api/events/getEvents
URI: 
Method: GET

--- GET EVENT BY ID ---

URI: http://localhost:3000/events/getEventById/{{eventId}}
Method: GET

--- UPDATE EVENT ---

URI: http://localhost:5000/service-event/api/events/updateEvent/69397cf5940163a625fe9f03
Method: PATCH

raw json:
    {
        "location": "Room C"
    }

--- DELETE EVENT ---

URI: http://localhost:5000/service-event/api/events/deleteEvent/{{eventId}}
Method: DELETE




--------------------------------------------------- RESERVATIONS ---------------------------------------------------------


